column5: I have a great life.  Parents who loved me, a wife who loves me, kids who are amazing.  Money isnt a problem, but I still sit around crippling depressed wishing i had meaning for life.  I suck I'm stupid  I have everything  I need and I know that, but I still wish I would die
I have kids. I would never kill myself for their sake, but if I didn't i would be long gone
